 class="t m0 x9 h4 y79 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">留在形象上，很难触及到佛法的本质。所以，真正的学佛，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y7a ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">必须要懂得佛教的教义，<span class="_ _4"></span>这对出家人、<span class="_ _6"></span>在家人来说，<span class="_ _4"></span>都不可</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yd6 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">缺少。<span class="_ _b"></span>否则，<span class="_ _b"></span>仅仅是佛教的个别行为，<span class="_ _b"></span>这些不能称之为正法。<span class="_ _8"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 y11f ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">鉴于此，<span class="_ _4"></span>近几年来，<span class="_ _6"></span>我们一直呼吁各地的在家男女、<span class="_ _4"></span>出</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y59 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">家人，<span class="_ _4"></span>务必要修学正法。<span class="_ _6"></span>毕竟佛教的意义相当深奥，<span class="_ _4"></span>没有系</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5a ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">统学习的话，<span class="_ _4"></span>不可能轻而易举就通达。<span class="_ _6"></span>像世间的学问，<span class="_ _4"></span>尚且</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5b ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">要依次读完小学、<span class="_ _6"></span>初中、<span class="_ _6"></span>高中，<span class="_ _6"></span>花费十多年的时间，<span class="_ _6"></span>一直学</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
